SOURCE https://techcrunch.com/2014/08/26/edgecase-relaunch/
AGENT Edgecase
GOAL Improve user experience while shopping online.
DATA Not Mentioned
METHODS Analyse the behaviour and actions of customers that signify commercial intent. Instead of just offering the choose brand and size options and limiting the search to that, egdecase employs a ranking system following your search patterns and offers a “More Like This” options.
RESULTS The company says that it was able to improve conversion rates for makeup retailer Urban Decay by 16 percent.
COMMENTS